00:19:19,040 --> 00:19:19,440
Enjoy your meal, sir.

569
00:19:19,600 --> 00:19:20,400
Please enjoy your meal, sir.

570
00:19:20,480 --> 00:19:21,840
You guys are looking at me eating.

571
00:19:51,680 --> 00:19:52,160
Comrades,

