our frugal canteen has just opened its first day today.

574
00:19:57,600 --> 00:19:58,480
But,

575
00:19:59,200 --> 00:20:01,600
first, we don't accept sympathy from others.

576
00:20:02,080 --> 00:20:03,920
second, we do not forgive bills.

577
00:20:05,040 --> 00:20:06,160
That Fu Sinian got up in the morning

578
