582
00:20:12,880 --> 00:20:13,680
Guo.

583
00:20:14,400 --> 00:20:15,360
You keep an eye on it.

584
00:20:15,520 --> 00:20:16,960
If someone doesn't pay for the meal today,

585
00:20:17,040 --> 00:20:18,080
don't let them out of this door.

586
00:20:18,400 --> 00:20:20,000
We must resolutely resist freeloading.

587
00:20:22,480 --> 00:20:23,280
Who are you talking about?

588
00:20:25,440 --> 00:20:26,320
What freeloading?

589
00:20:28,320 --> 00:20:29,440
What insinuating remarks.

590
00:20:29,600 --> 00:20:31,280
Why do you eat and eat, and yet are anxious?

591
00:20:32,160 --> 00:20:33,120
You don't have any money, do you?

592
00:20:33,920 --> 00:20:34,640
I- I- I-

593
