I left in a hurry. I forgot.

594
00:20:37,680 --> 00:20:38,560
That won't do.

595
00:20:39,120 --> 00:20:40,720
What should I do if you don't have any money?

596
00:20:41,440 --> 00:20:42,240
What can I do?

597
00:20:42,320 --> 00:20:43,200
I- I- I- I'll go back.

598
00:20:43,280 --> 00:20:45,040
I'm sure I'll give you the money then.

599
00:20:45,440 --> 00:20:46,240
How can I trust you?

600
00:20:46,400 --> 00:20:47,120
If you go out and run away,

601
00:20:47,360 --> 00:20:48,320
