823
00:29:44,080 --> 00:29:45,840
Of course, it's what our newspaper is interested in

824
00:29:46,320 --> 00:29:47,520
and reported before.

825
00:29:48,240 --> 00:29:49,600
Miss Liu, what about the list

826
00:29:49,760 --> 00:29:50,880
you provided this time?

827
00:29:51,040 --> 00:29:51,680
In principle?

828
00:29:51,920 --> 00:29:53,600
It can be classified as social news.

829
00:29:54,000 --> 00:29:55,200
We have no problem publishing it.

830
00:29:55,440 --> 00:29:58,000
However, the introduction of the canteen,

831
00:29:58,240 --> 00:29:58,800
laundry

832
00:29:58,960 --> 00:30:00,480
and film screening group you mentioned

833
00:30:00,720 --> 00:30:01,840
is actually in the advertising category.

834
00:30:02,160 --> 00:30:03,200
There is a fee.

835
00:30:03,600 --> 00:30:05,440
Miss Liu, did you know that?

836
00:30:07,600 --> 00:30:09,280
The Work-Study Mutual Aid Society is full of students.

837
00:30:09,760 --> 00:30:11,920
Work-study is a part-work and part-study programme.

838
